# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DO NOT hardcode the API Gateway URL here.
#
# On every `terraform apply`, the deploy_frontend null_resource (infra/addons.tf)
# injects the LIVE endpoint as REACT_APP_API_GATEWAY_URL at build time, so it
# always matches the current stack — even after destroy/recreate.
#
# This file only holds a local-dev fallback. When running `npm start` locally
# against a deployed backend, you may uncomment and set the line below:
#
# REACT_APP_API_GATEWAY_URL=https://your-api-id.execute-api.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
